234
00:18:42,041 --> 00:18:46,514
En serio, amigo.
Es hora de irse a la cama.

235
00:18:48,756 --> 00:18:50,224
Hola, Jenny Pen.

236
00:18:50,424 --> 00:18:52,101
Sí.
Buenas noches, Jenny Pen.

237
00:18:52,301 --> 00:18:54,228
